00:40:35,411 --> 00:40:36,844
Always remember us.

259
00:46:13,816 --> 00:46:14,942
My son...

260
00:46:22,291 --> 00:46:24,020
...you do not remember me.

261
00:46:25,628 --> 00:46:26,754
I am Jor-El.

262
00:46:28,531 --> 00:46:29,828
I am your father.

263
00:46:32,335 --> 00:46:34,963
By now you will have reached
your eighteenth year...

264
00:46:35,671 --> 00:46:37,298
...as it is measured on Earth.

265
00:46:38,507 --> 00:46:39,997
By that reckoning...

266
00:46:41,110 --> 00:46:44,136
...l will have been dead
for many thousands of your years.

267
00:46:46,716 --> 00:46:47,944
The knowledge...

268
00:46:49,218 --> 00:46:52,381
...that I have of matters,
physicalandhistorical...

269
00:46:52,888 --> 00:46:56,085
...I have given you fully on your voyage
